name: INGetCarPowerLevelStatusIntentResponseCode
desc: Constants that indicate the status of the response.

items.name: case failure
items.desc: An error code indicating that you were unable to get the car’s power level.

items.name: case failureRequiringAppLaunch
items.desc: An error code indicating that the user must launch your app to get the car’s current power level.

items.name: case inProgress
items.desc: A response code indicating that your app has requested the power level data, but has not yet received the results.

items.name: case ready
items.desc: A response code indicating that you are ready to handle the intent.

items.name: case success
items.desc: A response code indicating that you successfully handled the intent.

items.name: case unspecified
items.desc: A response code indicating that the status was not specified.
